\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Boston City Campus and Business College \'28Pty\'29 Ltd is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution has also applied for a Higher Certificate in South African Tourism and an Advanced Certificate in African and European Tourism. \cell \pard 

